title: Man-Cave | Watch: The biggest snake on record apparently caught on video - Is basically a dinosaur
text:
This is really the stuff that horror movies (and really crap B movies) are made from.
All that exists at the moment is the below video. It could very well be a hoax, we have no idea, but the snake appears to be dead and that has pissed off a lot of people in the comments section of the video. We don't know the context of what happened, if the person who captured it killed it, or if it was like that when they found it.
Regardless, if it is real, it is incredibly sad that the creature wasn't captured alive. Although, we wouldn't want to be in the same continent as it if it was.
Check it out for yourself
